Description: Include algorithm for std::remove in cppgc/stats-collector.h
 Newer libstdc++/compiler combinations no longer expose std::remove
 transitively through <vector>. Include <algorithm> directly to avoid
 resolving to C's remove() function from <cstdio>.
Author: Dockershelf Maintainers <41898282+github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
Forwarded: no

--- a/deps/v8/src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h
+++ b/deps/v8/src/heap/cppgc/stats-collector.h
@@ -9,6 +9,7 @@
 #include <stddef.h>
 #include <stdint.h>
 
+#include <algorithm>
 #include <atomic>
 #include <vector>
 
